title: Cube Commander
description: Cube Commander is an action game where you must battle against zombies and protect the innocent. Venture through various terrains, from forests to swamps, and even ice and hellfire, pushing your limits to the edge of the world. Rally brave soldiers and unleash their skills to fight off hordes of evil spirits. Upgrade your warriors across five levels, utilize the dynamite catapult for explosive destruction, ride dragons to rain down bombs, and mount animals for swift movement. Gather gold in chests to prepare for the next level. Can you triumph over the forces of darkness?
